{"word":"H7124 - קֹרֵא - qôrêʼ - ko-ray' - Partridge","slug":"H7124","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קֹרֵא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qôrêʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ko-ray'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Partridge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05E8;&#x05D0; - qo&#x0302;re&#x0302;'</b> - <i>ko-ray'</i><p/>Properly active participle of <a href=\"#/H7121\">H7121</a>; a <i>caller</i>, that is, <i>partridge</i> (from its <i>cry</i>): - partridge. See also <a href=\"#/H6981\">H6981</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4744\">H4744</a>, <a href=\"#/H6981\">H6981</a>, <a href=\"#/H7121\">H7121</a>, <a href=\"#/H7148\">H7148</a>, <a href=\"#/H7150\">H7150</a>"}]}